---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 557
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Grace=Necessity
  - 405
By: Sri Ramana Maharshi
---
Divine Grace is essential for Realisation. It leads one to
God-Realisation. But such Grace is vouchsafed only to him who is a
true devotee or a yogin, who has striven hard and ceaselessly on the
path towards freedom.
